{"tid":1356440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大件事】今次大家真玩大左！！！","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:37:30.000Z","uid":66271,"like":34,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf949e63a0dfb2b323f331751e1fce72670785c","tid":1356440,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"三上悠亞原定7.27率Honey Popcorn辦見面會 因香港局勢動盪取消<br />\n<br />\n由三上悠亞領軍的女團Honey Popcorn原定於7月27日在上環西港城舉行的《Honey Popcorn Fan Meeting In Hong Kong 2019》，主辦單位宣布因為近日香港局勢動盪而取消，現已開始與已購票的觀眾聯絡安排退票，這是繼7月初KAT-TUN之後，第二個因香港政局而取消來港的日本演藝組合。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3069886/org/d4cc154439940a2ee03ff99e6017e428.jpg/VcdzLIvYnAfu-jdZuuj8gB0Km6OdthaUDfaT3A32k9w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3069886%2Forg%2Fd4cc154439940a2ee03ff99e6017e428.jpg%2FVcdzLIvYnAfu-jdZuuj8gB0Km6OdthaUDfaT3A32k9w&h=e496abd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3069876/org/bb4548025c1416b56f892475986033e4.jpg/4nz5QMn1M8-wEEtRBgmXlYPhA-gjkh6fdpaXvXaWl70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3069876%2Forg%2Fbb4548025c1416b56f892475986033e4.jpg%2F4nz5QMn1M8-wEEtRBgmXlYPhA-gjkh6fdpaXvXaWl70&h=dde7e0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3069880/org/12263201741aee4dd8c216058d8d506c.jpg/ekaq_gE9S39afwJ5nJeYrVtRsk852PbhPspomD7KaJg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3069880%2Forg%2F12263201741aee4dd8c216058d8d506c.jpg%2Fekaq_gE9S39afwJ5nJeYrVtRsk852PbhPspomD7KaJg&h=22fab991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭你落台啦，比番三上悠亞我</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44790fdde69cb3e7f8ae0fe20843214c4e028bb9","tid":1356440,"uid":103759,"like":0,"disli